le inductive proofs are known, and the graphs ($k \\le\n6$) whose best spanning ratios have been established by complex arguments. Here\nwe reduce the known spanning ratio of $Y_6$ from $17.6$ to $5.8$, getting\ncloser to the spanning ratio of 2 established for $\\Theta_6$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2013 19:33:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Mar 2014 20:37:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2019 01:28:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-18"}
