idefinite relaxation (SDR). Then, the original problems are solved by a\none-dimension search over the optimal SINR target for ERs or IR. Furthermore,\nfor each of the two studied problems, suboptimal solutions of lower complexity\nare also proposed in which the information and energy beamforming vectors are\nseparately designed with their power allocation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 14:49:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jul 2013 05:49:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2014 07:40:54 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 08:32:27 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2014 15:23:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
